          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1411.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, cut the <strong>leek<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways and wash carefully to remove any grit from between the leaves, then top, tail and slice finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
