          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1411.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>mushroom & parsley orzo</strong> topped with the <strong>crispy chicken</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong>, garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped parsley </strong>and drizzle with some<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
